elog_lib v1.0.2 | Mar 07 2026:

-- Bug Fixes --
  [Fix] ELOG_AUDIT_FILE expansion in elog_init() changed from ${:-} to ${-}
      so consumers can set ELOG_AUDIT_FILE="" to disable audit logging
  [Fix] elog_logrotate_snippet() respects empty ELOG_AUDIT_FILE (omits from
      rotation config when audit is disabled)
  [Fix] Redundant local _fmt declarations in elog() backward-compat block
      consolidated to single declaration at block top
  [Fix] Comment on syslog_file module registration corrected from
      "receives all output" to "receives elog() output (source=elog)"

-- Documentation --
  [Change] SIEM extras space-delimiter limitation documented in elog_event()
      API comment, README, and at each SIEM parsing site (CEF, GELF, ELK)
  [New] Integration guide section in README with step-by-step embedding,
      elog() vs elog_event() decision tree, and consumer patterns (BFD/LMD/APF)
  [New] Configuration profiles section in README (development, production
      daemon, SIEM integration, monitoring-only)
  [New] Use cases section in README with real code snippets for firewall,
      intrusion detection, malware scanning, and SIEM forwarding
  [New] Troubleshooting section in README covering stdout, log files, SIEM
      delivery, audit log, and log growth issues
